\noindent{\textbf{Notation}\\[0.5em]
\textcolor{axis}{$\xi_i$}: Coordinate component $i$\\
\phantom{$\xi_i$:} E.g. $\underline{\xi} = [\xi_1, \xi_2]\Trans$\\[1em]
$\underline{\xi}_i$: Coordinates of vertex $i$\\
\phantom{$\underline{\xi}_i$:} E.g. $\underline{\xi}_1 = [-1, -1]\Trans$\\[1em]
\textcolor{facet}{$f_i$}: Facet (edge) nr $i$
